node.text:
I had such a wicked time on the weekend! I really missed being behind the wheel💖 

How fricken amazing do the new @heritagewheel Kokoro Mono-c wheels look on the 350! Such a great little event to run them in! Definitely turned a lot of heads haha. I can’t wait for @qrdriftmatsuri 💖

The car ran well, as always the @mcasuspension impresses me with how well it handles a beating. I definitely think the performance suspension helps so much doing this high intensity driving.

The gorgeous wrap by @exclusivewrapsaus is such a head turner! Thank you guys for accomodating my weeb needs and designing the perfect livery!

Also thank you to @jaxtyresrockhampton for always looking after me and my tyre fitting needs! I was running @nankangmotorsport AR1 Tyres on the front and Dynamo Tyres on the rear. 

And finally thank you to @fishandrifts for filming my runs for me! It’s so great to have friends running at events with me! 🔥🤟🏼
